Source: pgbouncer-fdw
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/CrunchyData/pgbouncer_fdw

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pgbouncer-fdw
Architecture: all
Provides: postgresql-pgbouncer-fdw
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: pgbouncer (>= 1.17)
Description: Query and control PgBouncer from PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 pgbouncer_fdw provides SQL views over PgBouncer SHOW commands and functions
 for administrative commands. It uses dblink_fdw to connect to one or more
 PgBouncer admin consoles.
